Drippic
=======
dependencies
-------------
content
content_copy
filefield
imagefield

It is important to make sure these are enabled before installing Drippic, to ensure the "pic" content type is copied correctly.

Comment module is not a dependency, but by enabling it and adding commenting to the "pic" content type you can allow commenting on your photos. These comments are sent back to Twitter as an @ reply to the photo author.

API References
--------------
* http://twitpic.com/api.do#upload
